# Admin frontend (Astro + Tailwind)

Read and follow `.cursor/skills/frontend-astro-tailwind/SKILL.md` when editing admin files.

- Reuse `src/components/admin/ui/*` primitives; do not duplicate input/button styles inline.
- Admin look: `bg-zinc-50` shell, white cards, `border-outline-variant`, no concert/dark public styles.
- Inputs `h-11`, tables in `Table.astro`, mobile actions `w-full sm:w-auto`.
- Do not change Supabase RPCs, auth middleware, or route paths in UI-only tasks.
